<GUIClass name="ITSSingleUserTestForm" id="3502913c-febe-46f0-9082-a12d8c2b4a32">
    <superclass name="Form"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Created this form when doing the initial testing of the ITS interface.
It initiates the three ITS controllers without the TCP connection and
is useful for debugging.

Used the form in a local copy of JMT.  In my local copy I would create
an application to run the form and would run the application in single
user mode with the debugger active.

The form is only used for internal testing so you are welcome to change it.</text>
